801
00:37:33,600 --> 00:37:35,200
 Da, sad si, sad si, daj.

802
00:37:35,200 --> 00:37:36,200
 Nima šta je novo,

803
00:37:36,200 --> 00:37:36,700
 nema ništa.

804
00:37:36,700 --> 00:37:37,840
 Znači, nema ništa novo,

805
00:37:37,840 --> 00:37:40,200
 o tom govorim

806
00:37:40,200 --> 00:37:40,640
 zadnjih, evo,

