811
00:37:44,420 --> 00:37:45,660
 u prosincu.

812
00:37:45,660 --> 00:37:47,380
 To je privatno vlasništvo

813
00:37:47,380 --> 00:37:48,880
 u stečaju,

814
00:37:48,880 --> 00:37:50,260
 da, i onda grad na taj način

815
00:37:50,260 --> 00:37:51,200
