974
00:41:08,820 --> 00:41:11,720
 Bojim se da je to nekako.

975
00:41:11,720 --> 00:41:12,920
 Ja, s obzirom kakav zakon

976
00:41:12,920 --> 00:41:14,720
 sad ovaj toplinari spremaju,

977
00:41:14,720 --> 00:41:16,680
 ono,

978
00:41:16,680 --> 00:41:19,120
 nema, mislim, znaš,

979
00:41:19,120 --> 00:41:19,740
 bilo bi lijepo,

