982
00:41:21,900 --> 00:41:22,840
 Ali dobro, vidiš.

983
00:41:22,840 --> 00:41:23,300
 S jedne strane,

984
00:41:23,300 --> 00:41:24,120
 glej, s jedne strane sam,

985
00:41:24,120 --> 00:41:24,880
 ovako, ajmo ovako reći.

986
00:41:27,120 --> 00:41:29,520
 Jer je to, ima potencijal

987
00:41:29,520 --> 00:41:30,420
 da bude dobra priča

988
00:41:30,420 --> 00:41:32,100
 u smislu energije

989
00:41:32,100 --> 00:41:32,860
 koja je,

990
00:41:32,860 --> 00:41:34,820
 koja je tako kakva je

991
00:41:34,820 --> 00:41:36,280
 ova geotermalna energia.

992
00:41:36,280 --> 00:41:37,580
 S druge strane,

993
00:41:37,580 --> 00:41:38,920
 sam pesimističan,

994
00:41:38,920 --> 00:41:40,340
 bar ne što se tiče

995
00:41:40,340 --> 00:41:41,220
 ove vlasti sada,

996
00:41:41,220 --> 00:41:42,780
 jer po meni

997
00:41:42,780 --> 00:41:44,300
 gradski sustav u širem smislu,

998
00:41:44,300 --> 00:41:45,840
 a to znači ne samo poglavarstvo,

999
00:41:45,840 --> 00:41:46,860
 nego i gradske ustanove,

1000
00:41:46,860 --> 00:41:47,580
 gradske tvrtke,

1001
00:41:47,580 --> 00:41:49,380
 a geotermika je jedna od njih,

1002
00:41:49,380 --> 00:41:51,760
