1003
00:41:51,760 --> 00:41:52,340
 i ne radi,

1004
00:41:52,340 --> 00:41:53,540
 nisu dobodno efikasni.

1005
00:41:53,540 --> 00:41:54,100
 Po meni,

1006
00:41:54,100 --> 00:41:55,400
 gradski sustav trebao biti

1007
00:41:55,400 --> 00:41:55,940
