1008
00:41:56,040 --> 00:41:56,860
 puno fleksibilniji,

1009
00:41:56,860 --> 00:41:57,860
 puno efikasniji

1010
00:41:57,860 --> 00:41:59,020
 i puno više

1011
00:41:59,020 --> 00:42:00,080
 na raspolaganju građanima.

1012
00:42:00,080 --> 00:42:00,800
 To mi malo,

1013
00:42:00,800 --> 00:42:01,540
