1030
00:42:18,160 --> 00:42:18,480
 recimo,

1031
00:42:18,480 --> 00:42:19,100
 isposlovanjem

1032
00:42:19,100 --> 00:42:19,820
 i s nekim drugim

1033
00:42:19,820 --> 00:42:20,820
