1034
00:42:20,820 --> 00:42:22,080
 prema ljudima,

1035
00:42:22,080 --> 00:42:23,040
 prema građanima,

1036
00:42:23,040 --> 00:42:24,640
 opet ostaje činjenica

1037
00:42:24,640 --> 00:42:26,060
 da oko,

1038
00:42:26,060 --> 00:42:26,360
 mislim,

1039
00:42:26,360 --> 00:42:26,780
 50,

1040
00:42:26,780 --> 00:42:28,160
 sad ne govorimo

1041
00:42:28,160 --> 00:42:29,360
 onima koji ne žele,

1042
00:42:29,360 --> 00:42:30,080
