1051
00:42:38,600 --> 00:42:39,240
 Ali ima,

1052
00:42:39,240 --> 00:42:40,840
 ali ogroman dio ljudi

1053
00:42:40,840 --> 00:42:41,300
 i na drva.

1054
00:42:41,300 --> 00:42:41,820
 Ti vani,

1055
00:42:41,820 --> 00:42:42,420
 kad dođeš u neke,

1056
00:42:42,420 --> 00:42:42,680
 recimo,

1057
00:42:42,680 --> 00:42:43,960
 razvijene gradove

1058
00:42:43,960 --> 00:42:44,500
 ili države,

1059
00:42:44,500 --> 00:42:45,400
 njima opće

1060
00:42:45,400 --> 00:42:46,700
