1065
00:42:52,380 --> 00:42:53,000
 Kvartovski,

1066
00:42:53,000 --> 00:42:54,700
 čak i zgrade neki.

1067
00:42:54,700 --> 00:42:56,480
 Mislim i naš zakon to dopušta.

1068
00:42:56,480 --> 00:42:57,460
 Da, moraš biti pokriven.

1069
00:42:57,460 --> 00:42:58,700
 Nismo ti to dali,

1070
00:42:58,700 --> 00:43:00,660
