00:55:25,280 --> 00:55:26,340
 Odnosno, jedan je bio, recimo,

1529
00:55:26,340 --> 00:55:27,040
 duplo niži.

1530
00:55:27,040 --> 00:55:29,200
 Međutim, taj nije ušao

1531
00:55:29,200 --> 00:55:30,260
