1555
00:56:02,760 --> 00:56:03,800
 Ja nisam protiv nebodera.

1556
00:56:03,940 --> 00:56:05,400
 Da je pitanje danas koliko uopće

1557
00:56:05,400 --> 00:56:07,340
 poželjno nebodera igrati.

1558
00:56:07,340 --> 00:56:07,700
 Znači, gledaj,

1559
00:56:07,700 --> 00:56:08,120
 s jedne strane,

1560
00:56:08,120 --> 00:56:10,840
 nisam protiv nebodera,

1561
00:56:10,840 --> 00:56:12,300
 što znači da ako se pokaže

1562
00:56:12,300 --> 00:56:13,220
 negdje prostor,

1563
00:56:13,220 --> 00:56:13,460
 ok,

1564
00:56:13,460 --> 00:56:14,200
 međutim,

1565
00:56:14,200 --> 00:56:14,520
 danas,

1566
00:56:14,520 --> 00:56:15,500
 što sam rekao,

1567
00:56:15,500 --> 00:56:17,400
 danas je situacija da se

1568
00:56:17,400 --> 00:56:18,760
 Karlovac može

1569
00:56:18,760 --> 00:56:20,840
 i mora razvijati u prostoru.

1570
00:56:20,840 --> 00:56:21,640
 To ja samo ponavljam.

1571
00:56:21,640 --> 00:56:23,600
 Karlovac se mora razvijati u prostoru,

1572
00:56:23,600 --> 00:56:24,600
 to znači manje zgrade,

1573
00:56:24,600 --> 00:56:25,500
 to znači širenje.

1574
00:56:25,500 --> 00:56:26,160
 Recimo,

1575
00:56:26,160 --> 00:56:26,940
 danas ti je znanstvena

1576
00:56:26,940 --> 00:56:27,660
 fantastika

1577
00:56:27,660 --> 00:56:29,080
 da se

1578
00:56:29,080 --> 00:56:30,640
