1585
00:56:35,240 --> 00:56:35,980
 igralište,

1586
00:56:35,980 --> 00:56:37,120
 prometnice.

1587
00:56:37,120 --> 00:56:38,520
 To je moguće.

1588
00:56:38,520 --> 00:56:38,940
 Da su mogli,

1589
00:56:38,940 --> 00:56:39,600
 Ljubovane Luščić,

1590
00:56:39,600 --> 00:56:40,520
